      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've honestly got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolute showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found! I've pampered this car since day one, and it still has that brand-new feel every time you get behind the wheel. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and is ready for a new home, this is the one. Come check it out, you\u2019re going to love it!",
